snippet.title: Amber Heard--Confessions of a Malignant Narcissist
snippet.description:
Regrettably, the second audio tape where Depp and Heard are on the phone during the divorce proceedings is rather unintelligible.  You can't really make out a word Amber's saying, but the point is not WHAT she is saying it's how she is saying it, and every calculated tone the narcissist takes to devalue their victims.
Shout outs to Autumn On Venus and Incredibly Average both for making amazing video breakdowns of these two audios.
For Incredibly Average's Channel-
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg0C-N_MPYYOXyF4T3jMxNQ
For Autumn On Venus's Channel-
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKwY6wt3swWB3a2NJyE6qpA
You all can find me on Twitter under @FantasyWeavers
My email is jyenkotah@keeptruthalive.org 
Thank you for watching and subscribing!  Your support means  a lot!!!  We're all in this together trying to survive narcissistic abuse and expose truth about the narcissists who hurt us and other good people.  Keep fighting and believing in truth!!!
